What if I told you

155
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:08,610
I admired
your boldly-applied makeup?

156
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,740
* Oh!

157
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:18,070
SHELDON:
Greetings from stall number one.

158
00:06:18,110 --> 00:06:20,640
As much as I detest
that odd-smelling cigarette,

159
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:21,880
I do applaud

160
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:24,020
